snippet.title: 【NINJA KATO 1】 pre-release play video.
snippet.description:
【NINJA KATO 1】 【Pre-release】【Play video】
We will be releasing a preview of the gameplay video of "NINJA KATO 1" scheduled to be released on December 8, 2023.


Sold on Steam, Epic Games, and Google Play!
●Steam
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2653330/NINJA_KATO_1/
●Epic Games
https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/ninja-kato-1-47e118?lang=en-US
●Google Play
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.KIBODO.NINJAKATO1
